@startuml CurrentUseCase
title Personalised News Aggregator - Current Use Cases (as implemented)
left to right direction

' ── Styling — matches use-case.puml for visual consistency ─────────────
skinparam DefaultFontName         "Segoe UI"
skinparam DefaultFontSize         12

skinparam Actor {
  BorderColor                     #1A252F
  BackgroundColor                 #D5E8D4
  FontStyle                       bold
  FontSize                        13
}

skinparam Usecase {
  BorderColor                     #1F618D
  BackgroundColor                 #EBF5FB
  BorderThickness                 1.5
  FontSize                        12
}

skinparam Rectangle {
  BorderColor                     #1A252F
  BorderThickness                 2
  BackgroundColor                 #FDFEFE
  FontStyle                       bold
  FontSize                        14
}

skinparam Arrow {
  Color                           #2C3E50
  FontSize                        11
  FontStyle                       italic
}

skinparam Note {
  BackgroundColor                 #FEF9E7
  BorderColor                     #F0B27A
}
' ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

actor "Visitor" as Visitor
actor "User"    as User
Visitor <|-- User

rectangle "News Aggregator System" {

  ' --- Account Management ---
  usecase "Register Account" as UC11a
  usecase "Log In"           as UC11b

  ' --- Core Content Interaction ---
  usecase "Browse Personalized Feed"    as UC1
  usecase "View Article"                as UC12
  usecase "Search & Filter Articles"    as UC5

  ' --- Article Enhancements (GenAI, all real endpoints) ---
  usecase "View AI Summary"           as UC2
  usecase "Get Concept Explanation"   as UC3
  usecase "View Sentiment & Bias"     as UC6
  usecase "Ask AI a Question (Q&A)"   as UC13

  ' --- User Library ---
  usecase "Save/Bookmark Article"  as UC7
  usecase "View Saved Articles"    as UC7b

  ' --- Preferences ---
  usecase "Manage Topic Preferences"      as UC14
  usecase "Subscribe/Unsubscribe Source"  as UC15

}

note right of UC15
  Sources are shared: subscriberCount is
  tracked server-side and a source is
  auto-removed once its last subscriber
  leaves.
end note

note bottom of UC6
  "Bias" is a categorical label
  (left | center | right | unclear),
  not a numeric bias score.
end note

' --- Actor Connections ---
Visitor --> UC11a
Visitor --> UC11b

User --> UC1
User --> UC5
User --> UC12
User --> UC7b
User --> UC14
User --> UC15

' --- Use Case Relationships ---
UC1 --> UC12  : <<include>>
UC5 --> UC12  : <<include>>

UC12 <.. UC2  : <<extend>>
UC12 <.. UC3  : <<extend>>
UC12 <.. UC6  : <<extend>>
UC12 <.. UC13 : <<extend>>
UC12 <.. UC7  : <<extend>>

note "Scoped out relative to the initial plan\n(no backend, or removed): Recommendations,\nTrending Topics (client-side re-sort of the\ncurrent page only, not a real ranking),\nNotifications (frontend-only mock, disclaimed\nin the UI), Auto-tag & Categorize (topicId\nexists but nothing ever sets it), Bookmark\nFolders (flat list only)." as N1
@enduml
